share_info: {'acl': {'code': 0, 'extra': '{}'}, 'desc': 'GRACE‚Äôs comment: I feel like it‚Äôs moreso the scale has shifted to whose body is more naturally attainable. text: One thing though back then even if you were skinny if you had the slightest bit of curviness to you then you were fat.
